  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/cd74d4920ec1e666819742c78cef7077.avif?t=1739061784\" width=600 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Ailuri </i></strong>is a 2D platformer, level based game with hand drawn art.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore levels at your own pace, survive against the dangers of the world and rescue other creatures in this heartbreaking story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.poster.avif?t=1739061784\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.webm?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.mp4?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level based gameplay, full of puzzles, difficult obstacles and hidden secrets for players of all types to encounter.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or with a companion in couch co-op. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through unique World Maps, explore vast Levels and defeat destructive Bosses. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grapple, Climb, Swing, Throw -  Defeat the invasive enemies to collect the Essence of the Forests, Waters and Mountains to unlock mystical Abilities!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.poster.avif?t=1739061784\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.webm?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.mp4?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/cd74d4920ec1e666819742c78cef7077.avif?t=1739061784\" width=600 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Ailuri </i></strong>is a 2D platformer, level based game with hand drawn art.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore levels at your own pace, survive against the dangers of the world and rescue other creatures in this heartbreaking story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.poster.avif?t=1739061784\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.webm?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/38c630cbec445d504e1890b9604be15a.mp4?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level based gameplay, full of puzzles, difficult obstacles and hidden secrets for players of all types to encounter.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or with a companion in couch co-op. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through unique World Maps, explore vast Levels and defeat destructive Bosses. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grapple, Climb, Swing, Throw -  Defeat the invasive enemies to collect the Essence of the Forests, Waters and Mountains to unlock mystical Abilities!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.poster.avif?t=1739061784\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.webm?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208690/extras/2faaf8fbac35b14b52e3976ad18d6589.mp4?t=1739061784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
